static NSString* const kStuffString = @"{\n    \"stories\": [\n        {\n            \"id\": 68728213,\n            \"path\": \"/business/68728213/Live-Chat-Bill-English-on-New-Zealand-Budget-2015\",\n            \"url\": \"http://www.stuff.co.nz/_json/business/68728213/Live-Chat-Bill-English-on-New-Zealand-Budget-2015\",\n            \"section\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"section-home\": \"Business\",\n            \"section-top-level\": \"Business\",\n            \"layout\": \"landscape-image\",\n            \"title\": \"Live Chat: Bill English on New Zealand Budget 2015\",\n            \"subhead\": null,\n            \"alt_headline\": \"Live Chat: Bill English\",\n            \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T153714+1200\",\n            \"datetime_display\": \"15:37 21/05/2015\",\n            \"byline\": null,\n            \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n            \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"category_id\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"stream_id\": \"stuff/business/68728213\",\n            \"intro\": \"Did you get all you hoped in the budget? Were you left sorely disappointed?\",\n            \"alt_intro\": \"Finance Minister Bill English will be joining us to answer your Budget day questions\",\n            \"body\": \"<p>Did you get all you hoped in the budget? Were you left sorely disappointed?<br /> <br /> Will the <a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68742199/budget-2015-benefits-rise-in-bid-to-tackle-child-poverty\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">$790 million package to lift 190,000 children out of poverty</a> work, or is it flawed? Is it fair to send sole-parents back to part time work before their youngest children have hit school?<br /> <br /> Perhaps the 430 hectares in Crown land to be freed up in Auckland for more houses, has given you glimmer of hope to get in the market, but you're unsure of the details.<br /> <br /> Has enough money gone to <a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68702774/budget-2015-education--whats-in-it-for-schools\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">education</a> and <a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68742541/budget-2015-health-gets-billiondollar-shot-in-the-arm\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">health</a> - the sectors that year-on-year require the biggest spends?<br /> <br /> The Budget's numbers are huge, but we've got the man at the helm to answer your questions from 4.30pm.<br /> <br /> Join us then when Finance Minister Bill English will be chatting live with the readers. You can submit your questions in the box below from 4.15pm.<br /> <br /> <b>BUDGET DETAILS:<br /> *&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68729413/new-zealands-2015-budget.html\\\">Full wrap of the Budget 2015<br /> </a>*&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68742199/budget-2015-benefits-rise-in-bid-to-tackle-child-poverty\\\">Benefits rise in bid to tackle child poverty<br /> </a>*&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68702774/budget-2015-education--whats-in-it-for-schools\\\">Education - what's in it for schools?<br /> </a>*&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68702261/budget-2015-national-makes-some-concessions-but-also-gets-tough\\\">Opinion: National makes some concessions but also gets tough<br /> </a>*&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68741678/budget-2015-modest-tax-cuts-flagged-for-2017\\\">Modest tax cuts flagged for 2017<br /> </a>*&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/68736405/budget-live-stream.html\\\">Watch the Budget speech and debate live in Parliament</a></b></p><p><div style='display:none;'>Live Blog Live Chat: Bill English</div><div id='cil-root-stream-c76b1fd794' class='cil-root'><span class='cil-config-data' title='{\\\"altcastCode\\\":\\\"c76b1fd794\\\",\\\"server\\\":\\\"www.coveritlive.com\\\",\\\"geometry\\\":{\\\"width\\\":\\\"fit\\\",\\\"height\\\":\\\"infinite\\\"},\\\"configuration\\\":{\\\"newEntryLocation\\\":\\\"top\\\",\\\"commentLocation\\\":\\\"top\\\",\\\"replayContentOrder\\\":\\\"chron