fern and Maori design.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814318,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166930/318/11814318.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"59\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814319,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T120850+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"12:08 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Kvraco/ Instagram\",\n                    \"caption\": \"An ad posted on Instagram of a martial arts kimono adorned with a silver fern and Maori design.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814319,\n                            \"layout\": \"Standard Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166930/319/11814319.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"620\",\n                            \"height\": \"348\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814320,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T120851+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"12:08 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Kvraco/ Instagram\",\n                    \"caption\": \"An ad posted on Instagram of a martial arts kimono adorned with a silver fern and Maori design.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814320,\n                            \"layout\": \"Strap Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166931/320/11814320.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"300\",\n                            \"height\": \"199\"\n                        },\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814321,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166931/321/11814321.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814322,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T120851+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"12:08 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Kvraco/ Instagram\",\n                    \"caption\": \"An ad posted on Instagram of a martial arts kimono adorned with a silver fern and Maori design.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814322,\n                            \"layout\": \"Defcon Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166931/322/11814322.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"418\",\n                            \"height\": \"219\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"id\": 68730998,\n            \"path\": \"/life-style/home-property/68730998/Harcourts-conference-tweets-hijacked\",\n            \"url\": \"http://www.stuff.co.nz/_json/life-style/home-property/68730998/Harcourts-conference-tweets-hijacked\",\n            \"section\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"section-home\": \"Home & Property\",\n            \"section-top-level\": \"Life & Style\",\n            \"layout\": \"landscape-image\",\n            \"title\": \"Harcourts conference tweets hijacked\",\n            \"subhead\": null,\n            \"alt_headline\": \"'Leaky home? Built-in water feature' \",\n            \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T115829+1200\",\n            \"datetime_display\": \"11:58 21/05/2015\",\n            \"byline\": \"JACK VAN BEYNEN\",\n            \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n            \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"category_id\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"stream_id\": \"stuff/life-style/home-property/68730998\",\n            \"intro\": \"Real estate agents. We love to hate 'em.\",\n            \"alt_intro\": \"Harcourts' Twitter hashtag has been hijacked - with hilarious results.\",\n            \"body\": \"<p>Real estate agents. We love to hate 'em.</p> <p>At least, that seems to be the feeling behind the trending Twitter tag #harcourtsconference.</p> <p>The tag, originally used by staff attending the 2015 Harcourts Conference at SkyCity in Auckland this week to share inspirational quotes from speakers, was hijacked by Twitter users on Wednesday night to mock the real estate profession.</p> <p>With the red-hot and ultra competitive state of the property market, it's no surprise real estate professionals are now wearing a target.</p> <p>The tweets subvert the kind of bland business advice Harcourts was tweeting, instead playing up tropes of the stereotypical real estate agent: dishonesty, wealth and greed.</p> <p>Harcourts CEO Hayden Duncan said the company wasn't taking the tweets too seriously.</p> <p>&quot;I don't think it's been hijacked, I think there's a great conversation going on,&quot; he said.</p> <p>&quot;We're glad people have joined the conversation, and as much as we take what we do seriously ... we also have a great sense of humour.&quot;</p> <p>He said laughter was one of Harcourts' four core values.</p> <p>Harcourts would look at responding to some of the tweets today, he said.</p> <p>But social media expert Wendy Thompson thinks Harcourts might have left its response too late.</p> <p>Thompson, who is managing Director at Auckland social media marketing company Socialites, said Harcourts could have won public favour by engaging in the banter on Twitter.<br /> <br /> &quot;It's a shame they didn't start bantering ... they've definitely missed an opportunity there.&quot;<br /> <br /> She said Twitter's instantaneous nature meant it was now &quot;probably too late&quot; for Harcourts to get involved.<br /> <br /> But their original idea was a sound one, Thompson said.<br /> <br /> &quot;Tweeting quotable quotes is exactly what you do at conferences.&quot;</p> <p>Any damage to Harcourts' image was mitigated by the way the tweets targeted the real estate profession generally rather than Harcourts as a company, she said.</p><p><blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">A view of a meth lab is still a view <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a></p>&mdash; Patrick Paul (@PatricklePaul) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/PatricklePaul/status/601114558309109760\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote> <script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">If you get caught on hidden camera sniffing the vendor&#39;s underwear just say you were looking for a hankie <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a></p>&mdash; Rachel Stewart (@RFStew) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/RFStew/status/600874390947909632\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Leaky home? More like built-in water feature, AM I RIIIGHT?? <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a></p>&mdash; Clint Roberts (@kiaoraclint) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/kiaoraclint/status/600862181249286144\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Forget your lunch? Turn up early for the open home and steal from the pantry <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a></p>&mdash; Sharyn Casey (@ShakefieldCasey) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/ShakefieldCasey/status/600859585826553856\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">&quot;Content not nontent&quot;the real <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a> tweets are better than the fake ones: <a href=\\\"https://t.co/p94bvCKF0s\\\">https://t.co/p94bvCKF0s</a></p>&mdash; Guy Williams (@guywilliamsguy) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/guywilliamsguy/status/600866062746259456\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script></p><p><blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Get the right team behind you and demand perfection in the details - Alison Aitken <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a></p>&mdash; Harcourts_Int (@Harcourts_Int) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/Harcourts_Int/status/600858039265193984\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">&quot;You need to have a plan for your future because it is where you will spend the rest of your life&quot; <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/JoCliffordRE\\\">@JoCliffordRE</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HarcourtsConference?src=hash\\\">#HarcourtsConference</a></p>&mdash; Katie McAleese (@katiemcaleese) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/katiemcaleese/status/600855024239906816\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Understand your numbers and taxes. You can stay poor trying to look rich. - John McFadden. <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a></p>&mdash; Harcourts_Int (@Harcourts_Int) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/Harcourts_Int/status/600856122615017472\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n</p><p><blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Plenty lols at <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a> - purge your frustration at being in the housing market/hearing about it/having ever dealt with an agent</p>&mdash; Emma Espiner (@emmawehipeihana) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/emmawehipeihana/status/600879702203453440\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script></p><p><blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">&quot;Laughter is the shortest distance between two people&quot;. Great to see laughter included in our Harcourts values. <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HarcourtsConference?src=hash\\\">#HarcourtsConference</a></p>&mdash; Katie McAleese (@katiemcaleese) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/katiemcaleese/status/600810157971386368\\\">May 19, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Great to see the hashtag helping spread one of our core values &#39;fun and laughter&#39; <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/harcourtsconference?src=hash\\\">#harcourtsconference</a> - some of these are great!</p>&mdash; Harcourts NZ (@HarcourtsNZ) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/HarcourtsNZ/status/601154179042803713\\\">May 20, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script></p>\",\n            \"images\": [\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814154,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T115902+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:59 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Spark Digital/Twitter\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Twitter users have hijacked the hashtag used to tweet highlights from 2015 Harcourts Conference.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814154,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166342/154/11814154.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814155,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T115902+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:59 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Spark Digital/Twitter\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Twitter users have hijacked the hashtag used to tweet highlights from 2015 Harcourts Conference.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814155,\n                            \"layout\": \"Standard Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166342/155/11814155.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"620\",\n                            \"height\": \"349\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814156,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T115902+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:59 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Spark Digital/Twitter\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Twitter users have hijacked the hashtag used to tweet highlights from 2015 Harcourts Conference.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814156,\n                            \"layout\": \"Strap Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166342/156/11814156.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"300\",\n                            \"height\": \"199\"\n                        },\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814157,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166342/157/11814157.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814158,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T115902+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:59 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Spark Digital/Twitter\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Twitter users have hijacked the hashtag used to tweet highlights from 2015 Harcourts Conference.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814158,\n                            \"layout\": \"Defcon Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166342/158/11814158.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"418\",\n                            \"height\": \"220\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814159,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T115902+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:59 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Spark Digital/Twitter\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Twitter users have hijacked the hashtag used to tweet highlights from 2015 Harcourts Conference.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814159,\n                            \"layout\": \"ipad section splash 956:956\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432166342/159/11814159.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"953\",\n                            \"height\": \"956\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"id\": 68725987,\n            \"path\": \"/world/europe/68725987/Hatton-Garden-jewel-heist-net-widens-with-new-arrest\",\n            \"url\": \"http://www.stuff.co.nz/_json/world/europe/68725987/Hatton-Garden-jewel-heist-net-widens-with-new-arrest\",\n            \"section\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"section-home\": \"Europe\",\n            \"section-top-level\": \"World\",\n            \"layout\": \"landscape-image\",\n            \"title\": \"Hatton Garden jewel heist net widens with new arrest\",\n            \"subhead\": null,\n            \"alt_headline\": \"Hatton Garden jewel heist net widens\",\n            \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T111122+1200\",\n            \"datetime_display\": \"11:11 21/05/2015\",\n            \"byline\": \"ROSANNA PRICE\",\n            \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n            \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n            \"intro\": \"British police have arrested another suspect in connection with the £60 million (NZ$127 million) robbery of Hatton Garden safety deposit boxes.\",\n            \"alt_intro\": \"Another suspect, a plumber, has been arrested in connection with the daring London £200 million robbery.\",\n            \"body\": \"<p>British police have arrested&nbsp;another suspect in connection with the &pound;60 million (NZ$127 million) robbery of Hatton Garden safety deposit boxes.</p> <p>Enfield plumber&nbsp;Hugh Doyle&nbsp;was arrested on Tuesday in a series of raids by around 200 police officers, the&nbsp;<i><a href=\\\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11617620/Plumber-with-pilots-licence-arrested-over-Hatton-Garden-heist.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Telegraph</a></i>&nbsp;reported.</p> <p>The&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/67974851/Hatton-Garden-jewel-heist-New-pictures-show-how-robbers-stole-116m-on-Easter\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">mysterious robbery had taken place over Easter weekend</a>, where there were no signs of forced entry into the premises but around 70 safety deposit boxes were broken into. The elaborate plan involved disabling the lift and drilling holes through concrete into the vault.</p> <p><b>READ MORE:<br /> *&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/68690655/father-and-son-car-dealers-are-suspects-in-hatton-garden-heist\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Father and son car dealers are suspects in Hatton Garden heist</a><br /> *&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/67974851/Hatton-Garden-jewel-heist-New-pictures-show-how-robbers-stole-116m-on-Easter\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Hatton Garden jewel heist: New pictures show how robbers stole $116m on Easter</a><br /> * <a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/67704619/jewel-thieves-use-wheelie-bin-to-escape-with-116-million-haul-during-twoday-heist\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Jewel thieves use wheelie bin to escape with $116 million haul during two-day heist</a></b></p> <p>Doyle is reported to be a 48-year-old married father of two, with a a passion for flying and yachting.</p> <p>Police raided 12 properties across London and Kent on Tuesday morning, and Doyle was one of a total of nine men arrested.</p> <p>His arrest stunned neighbours who described him as a popular, helpful and friendly man.</p> <p>One elderly neighbour told the&nbsp;<i>Telegraph&nbsp;</i>she had been shocked to hear that Doyle was among those being questioned in connection with the heist.</p> <p>&quot;Everyone knows him. The local pub knows him very well. He was not a bad man, he was a helpful person always willing to lend a hand.</p> <p>&quot;I am just very surprised. We are shocked that this has happened to us. He has two lovely kids and I am so sorry for his wife.&quot;</p> <p>Two other suspects are known to be a&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/68690655/father-and-son-car-dealers-are-suspects-in-hatton-garden-heist\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">father and son duo</a>,&nbsp;Brian Reader, 76, his 50-year-old son, also named Brian.</p>\",\n            \"images\": [\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11812758,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T095109+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"09:51 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Facebook\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Neighbours of the friendly plumber are shocked he has been arrested in connection with the heist.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812758,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/758/11812758.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11812759,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T095109+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"09:51 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Facebook\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Neighbours of the friendly plumber are shocked he has been arrested in connection with the heist.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812759,\n                            \"layout\": \"Standard Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/759/11812759.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"620\",\n                            \"height\": \"349\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11812760,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T095109+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"09:51 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Facebook\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Neighbours of the friendly plumber are shocked he has been arrested in connection with the heist.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812760,\n                            \"layout\": \"Strap Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/760/11812760.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"300\",\n                            \"height\": \"199\"\n                        },\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812761,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432158669/761/11812761.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11812762,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T095109+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"09:51 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Facebook\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Neighbours of the friendly plumber are shocked he has been arrested in connection with the heist.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812762,\n                            \"layout\": \"Defcon Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/762/11812762.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"418\",\n                            \"height\": \"219\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11812763,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T095109+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"09:51 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Facebook\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Neighbours of the friendly plumber are shocked he has been arrested in connection with the heist.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812763,\n                            \"layout\": \"ipad section splash 956:956\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/763/11812763.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"956\",\n                            \"height\": \"956\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11812764,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T095110+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"09:51 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"Roger Howarth/ Wikipedia\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"fairfax-media\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Fairfax Media\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Hatton Garden is most famous for being London’s jewellery quarter and centre of the UK diamond trade.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11812764,\n                            \"layout\": \"Standard Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/764/11812764.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"620\",\n                            \"height\": \"348\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11814044,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T114842+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:48 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"HANDOUT\",\n                    \"caption\": \"A combination of images from closed circuit television shows the robbery at Hatton Garden Safety Deposit Ltd. over the Easter weekend between April 2 and 4.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11814044,\n                            \"layout\": \"Standard Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432165722/044/11814044.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"620\",\n                            \"height\": \"348\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"id\": 68731268,\n            \"path\": \"/entertainment/tv-radio/68731268/Guy-gets-stood-up-and-then-rejected-on-Graham-Norton-Show\",\n            \"url\": \"http://www.stuff.co.nz/_json/entertainment/tv-radio/68731268/Guy-gets-stood-up-and-then-rejected-on-Graham-Norton-Show\",\n            \"section\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"section-home\": \"TV & Radio\",\n            \"section-top-level\": \"Entertainment\",\n            \"layout\": \"landscape-video\",\n            \"title\": \"Guy gets stood up and then rejected on Graham Norton Show\",\n            \"subhead\": null,\n            \"alt_headline\": \"Is this the worst rejection ever?\",\n            \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T111057+1200\",\n            \"datetime_display\": \"11:10 21/05/2015\",\n            \"byline\": null,\n            \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n            \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"category_id\": \"Stuff\",\n            \"stream_id\": \"stuff/entertainment/tv-radio/68731268\",\n            \"intro\": \"A wannabe Romeo was left red-faced in Graham Norton's red chair after he got dumped by his date - literally.\",\n            \"alt_intro\": \"A wannabe Romeo was left red-faced in Graham Norton's red chair after he got dumped by his date - literally.\",\n            \"body\": \"<p>A wannabe Romeo was left red-faced in Graham Norton's red chair after he got dumped by his date - literally.</p> <p>Thomas had asked Jessica out on a date, only to be refused because she wanted to go to the Graham Norton Show to see Kylie Minogue.</p> <p><b>READ MORE:<br /> <br /> *&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/66934757/He-peed-in-my-shoes-tale-by-Southland-girl-revealed-in-Graham-Nortons-Red-Chair\\\">'He peed in my shoes' tale by Southland girl revealed in Graham Norton's Red Chair</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> *&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/10047770/Kiwi-survives-Graham-Nortons-red-chair\\\">Kiwi survives Graham Norton's red chair</a>&nbsp;<br /> *&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/10609793/Kiwi-lad-catches-Taylor-Swifts-eye\\\">Kiwi lad catches Taylor Swift's eye&nbsp;<br /> </a>*&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/books/62716566/graham-norton-doesnt-know-how-kiwis-get-in-his-chair\\\">Graham Norton doesn't know how Kiwis get in his chair<br /> <br /> </a></b>Little did Jessica know Thomas had also arranged to come on the show, appearing on Norton's notorious red chair in the hopes of rescheduling the date on national television.<br /> <br /> &quot;I asked a girl out a couple of weeks ago and she said yes,&quot; said Thomas, as Kylie gasped and Jessica looked mortified.</p> <p>&quot;She cancelled on me once and we rescheduled for tonight and she cancelled on me again so she could come here and watch Kylie Minogue. As I had no plans for tonight I thought I'd come down here and see if she wanted to rearrange for next week.&quot;</p> <p>Jessica then had to decide whether to flip Thomas or let him walk. To the shock of the audience, she made the ruthless decision to flip him.</p> <p>As Norton said, Thomas was &quot;literally dumped&quot;.<br /> <br /> But the story had a happy ending. On Twitter, it emerged that Thomas and Jessica had in fact rescheduled their date - and there were no hard feelings between the pair.</p> <p>&quot;I don't hold anything against Jessica,&quot; Thomas tweeted.<br /> <br /> &quot;She's actually lovely. We have rearranged the date for Tuesday.&quot;</p> <p><a href=\\\"https://www.facebook.com/GossipStuff?ref=hl\\\"><b>Head to our Facebook page for more from Stuff Entertainment</b></a></p><p><blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">I don&#39;t hold anything against Jessica. She&#39;s actually lovely. We have rearranged the date for Tuesday. <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/RedChair?src=hash\\\">#RedChair</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GrahamNorton?src=hash\\\">#GrahamNorton</a></p>&mdash; Thomas Hewitt (@TJ_Hewitt) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/TJ_Hewitt/status/599343799064776705\\\">May 15, 2015</a></blockquote> <script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script>\\n\\n<blockquote class=\\\"twitter-tweet\\\" lang=\\\"en\\\"><p lang=\\\"en\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">She gave in &amp; took him for a drink! <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/grahnort\\\">@grahnort</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/McInTweet\\\">@McInTweet</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/jrwolstenholme\\\">@jrwolstenholme</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/jessicaanneball\\\">@jessicaanneball</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/Firthy1981\\\">@Firthy1981</a> <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/kylieminogue\\\">@kylieminogue</a> <a href=\\\"http://t.co/LW96u3gPSp\\\">pic.twitter.com/LW96u3gPSp</a></p>&mdash; Helen Woolf (@helenwoolf) <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/helenwoolf/status/598941598920134657\\\">May 14, 2015</a></blockquote>\\n<script async src=\\\"http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"></script></p>\",\n            \"images\": [\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11813711,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T111115+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:11 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"THE GRAHAM NORTON SHOW\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Getting turned down can be a nightmare for most people but ever wondered what it would be like to get turned down on national television? Wonder no more...\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11813711,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432163475/711/11813711.jpg\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11813712,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T111115+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:11 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"YouTube\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Thomas took a literal dumping when he tried to win over his crush on Graham Norton's red chair.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11813712,\n                            \"layout\": \"Small Thumbnail\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432163475/712/11813712.png\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"90\",\n                            \"height\": \"60\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11813713,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T111115+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:11 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"YouTube\",\n                    \"source_code\": \"1national-newsroom\",\n                    \"source_name\": \"Stuff\",\n                    \"caption\": \"Thomas took a literal dumping when he tried to win over his crush on Graham Norton's red chair.\",\n                    \"variants\": [\n                        {\n                            \"id\": 11813713,\n                            \"layout\": \"Standard Image\",\n                            \"src\": \"http://static2.stuff.co.nz/1432163475/713/11813713.png\",\n                            \"media_type\": \"Photo\",\n                            \"width\": \"620\",\n                            \"height\": \"349\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"id\": 11813714,\n                    \"datetime_iso8601\": \"20150521T111116+1200\",\n                    \"datetime_display\": \"11:11 21/05/2015\",\n                    \"creditline\": \"YouTube\",\n           